<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Everywhere" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Everywhere,</orth> 1) in every place: <bibl n="shak. son 84.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 84, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.97.4" default="NO" valid="yes">97, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.100.12" default="NO" valid="yes">100, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.102.4" default="NO" valid="yes">102, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.2.82" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 2, 82</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.1.44" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 1, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.235.44" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 235</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.2.72" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 2, 72</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.4.87" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 4, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.2.39" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 2, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.5.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 5, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 4, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.138" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 138</bibl> <emph>(of here and e.;</emph> cf. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.235" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 235</bibl>).<lb />2) to every place: <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 2.4.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. II, 4, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.1.124" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 1, 124</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.3.57" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 3, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 1, 2</bibl>.
<lb />3) in every part, thoroughly, altogether: <cit><quote>beauty o'ersnowed, and bareness e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 5, 8</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>ill faced, worse bodied, shapeless e.,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.2.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 2, 20</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the boy Love is perjured e.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.241" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 241</bibl></cit>. cf. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.256" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 256</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>